  "texts": [
    "Sixthly, AUC-ROC is the area under the receiver operating characteristic (ROC) curve.",
    "It is a measure of the model's ability to distinguish between positive and negative examples.",
    "The ROC curve plots the true positive rate (TPR) against the false positive rate (FPR) for different threshold values.",
    "The AUC-ROC is computed as the area under the ROC curve.",
    "Lastly, AUC-PR: AUC-PR is the area under the precision-recall curve."
  ],
